name: Sensfrx
summary: Advanced Fraud Detection SDK for iOS Applications
description:
SensFRX SDK is a comprehensive fraud detection solution for iOS applications. 
It provides advanced security mechanisms to prevent unauthorized access, detect 
fraudulent activities, and enhance app security against emulators, botnets, 
GPS spoofing, automated scripts, and device tampering. The SDK supports both 
Swift and Objective-C and integrates seamlessly with existing app architectures.
